tag_list: kaptain cadillac deville 1974 booty call ghetto tech ghettotech paris detroit 313 jit juke bass bootybass
description:
Kaptain Cadillac - Deville 1974

Label : BOOTY CALL RECORDS
Catalogue number : BCR 0015
Format :  Digital
Relase date : 02/06/2012
Tittle : Deville 1974	
Artists : Kaptain Cadillac, Six Foe

Tracklist:
01 - Kaptain Cadillac - Ghetto Zoo
02 - Kaptain Cadillac - Bounce and Bang
03 - Kaptain Cadillac - Booty Up Booty Down feat Six Foe

Eng: 
French ghetto pioneer and European Booty Bass unquestioned godfather, Kaptain Cadillac offers us a second EP, a personal and modern vision of ghetto tech. Within a street and shifted musical universe, his sound reflects the US Midwest influences mixed with Europeans club tones all of it served in a storm of BPM. Together reverent of his roots and innovative, the Cadillac sound approaches ghetto-tech as a unique style in permanent evolution. 

Composed of three original tracks, this EP kicks off with the beastly “Ghetto Zoo” giving the club a furious bestiary look wakening up the bassthirst sleeping in all of us. Then come “Bounce & Bang” a punch with its frenetic arpeggios, in the fine ghetto-tech tradition made in Detroit.  Ending with “Booty Up Booty Down” featuring Six Foe, the legendary Detroit MC from Databass Records chanting a furious burning calories anthem on well caliber synthesizers to move the most uncooperative booties. 

Optimized for the moistest dancefloors around the world, this EP puts Booty Bass back into the center of worldwide bass musics and confirms Kaptain Cadillac’s as highly ranked in international clubbing scene. 


Fr:
Pionnier ghetto francophone et parrain incontesté de la Booty Bass Européenne, Kaptain Cadillac nous livre avec ce deuxième maxi, une vision toute personnelle et contemporaine de la ghetto tech. Avec un univers musical street et décallé, sa musique est à la fois le reflet des influences du midwest des Etats-Unis et des sonorités club Européennes le tout servi dans une tempete de BPM. A la fois respectueuse de ses racines et innovante, le son cadillac aborde la ghetto-tech comme un style a part entière et en constante évolution.
 
Composé de trois titres originaux, ce EP ouvre les hostilités avec le bestiale "Ghetto Zoo", donnant au club des allures de bestiaire endiablé faisant ressortir l'animal assoifé de bass qui sommeille en chacun de nous. S'en suit un crochet du gauche avec "Bounce & Bang" et ses arpèges frénétiques, dans la plus pure tradition ghetto-tech made in Detroit. Pour finir avec un "Booty Up Booty Down" en featuring avec Six Foe, le légendaire MC de Detroit (Databass Records) scandant un hymne ravageur au brûlage de calories sur des synthés calibrés pour faire remuer les bootys les plus récalcitrants.
 
Optimisé pour les dancefloors les plus moites du globe, ce EP remet la Booty Bass au centre des bass-musics mondiales et confirme le statut de haut gradé du clubbing international de Kaptain Cadillac.



Supported By: Feadz, Schlachthofbronx, DJ Godfather, Nic Sarno, Chrissy Murderbot, DJ Zegon, Maddjazz, Sinjin Hawke OG Bulldog

description: Fresh from self releasing his lo-fi mixtape "CHAMPAGNE", ZEBRA KATZ serves you his debut release, Ima Read feat. Njena Reddd Foxxx on Mad Decent's Jeffree's Imprint. Pulling from a multimedia /performance art background, Zebra Katz brings a slo-mo dark delivery to his rhymes set over a the minimal unencumbered beat on "Ima Read".But what does "Ima Read" even mean? Simply put, "reading" is an old voguing term describing someone verbally insulting an opponent about something not so apparent to the average viewer. A good reader could tear you apart with one simply sentence. We were very luck to have such a varied selection remixes from the likes of J-Wow of Buraka Som Sistema, MIkeQ and B.Ames, Slick Shoota and Dj Sliink. A little bit of something for everyone on this one, look out for more from Zebra Katz, he's on the rise. Download via Hulkshare : http://hulkshare.com/i7pdydyrlldr Visit thejeffrees.com to download all past Jeffree releases! Zebra Katz Facebook Twitter Soundcloud
title: Zebra Katz - Ima Read feat. Njena Reddd Foxxx (J-Wow Remix)
